        <p class="from-left sliders layout" style="background-color: white; color: black">
            <span>Brief Description of Sport</span> Badminton is an indoor sport that is played on a rectangular court measuring 44 feet x 17 feet (13.4 x 5.18 meters) for a singles match which is one player per side. And the court for doubles (two players
            per side) is 44 feet x 20 feet (13.4 x 6.1 meters).
        </p>
    </div>
    <!--content2-->
    <div class="grid">
        <p class="from-left sliders layout" style="background-color: white; color: black">
            <span>The Goal of Sport</span> The goal of the sport is to try to hit the shuttlecock to the ground on the other side of the net while trying to keep the shuttlecock from landing on your side of the court.
        </p>
        <p class="from-left sliders title" style="background-color: rgb(22, 97, 82);">
            <br>
            <img class='images' src="https://blog.playo.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/970a69bbe6e6f6b1b425fc97719c5d240de9b19b.jpg" alt="images">
        </p>
    </div>
    <!--content3-->
    <div class="grid">
        <p class="from-left sliders title" style="background-color: rgb(22, 97, 82);">
